data.description:
Stunning 3-bedroom, 2-story home in a gated community in North LV.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting foyer that leads to an open-concept living area. The spacious living room is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance for gatherings with family and friends.  Prepare to impress with the gourmet kitchen featuring elegant granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, you'll find the well-appointed bedrooms, each offering ample space and plenty of natural light. The master suite is a true sanctuary with a glass-enclosed shower, and dual vanities. Living in this gated community provides an added layer of security and peace of mind. Conveniently located near excellent schools, shopping centers, and major transportation routes, this home offers the ideal combination of tranquility and accessibility.

Don't miss this incredible opportunity and schedule a tour today to make this your forever home!
